text: Ayni≈üan Quliyeva (born 1992 in Baku, Azerbaijan) is a singer. She is the daughter of Azeri singer Aybeniz Hasimova. In 2010 she made it to the Azerbaijani national final for the chance to represent Azerbaijan in the Eurovision Song Contest in 2011 held in Germany.Eurovision Song Contest 2022 news by esctoday - Turin Italy In her semifinal she received 25000 votes, about 10000 more votes then any of the other winners of the semifinals.
